---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Saar Paamoni — Product leader, artist, surfer, builder, dad.">
    <article class="post-content no-image">
        <div class="about-body">
            <img src="/img/about-portrait.jpg" alt="Saar Paamoni" class="about-float-photo" />

            <h1 class="about-title">About</h1>

            <p class="about-lead">
                I build products, paint on weekends, catch waves badly,
                and prioritize being a present dad.
            </p>

            <p>
                Powered through the last decade as Product at DoubleVerify (NYSE:DV) — leading measurement
                and verification across CTV, display, video, and mobile at a scale
                of billions of signals per day. I know the ad ecosystem from every angle:
                DSPs, SSPs, publishers, agencies, standards bodies. More importantly,
                I know where the real opportunities are hiding.
            </p>

            <p>
                These days I advise founders and operators building at the intersection of
                AI, media, and measurement — and I'm quietly building something of my own.
            </p>

            <h2>Making things</h2>
            <p>
                Outside of product work, I paint. Acrylic on canvas, mostly — bold,
                textured, warm. Painting is my way of thinking without language. It's
                what I do when I want to be fully present without an agenda.
            </p>
            <p>
                I also surf, badly and happily, whenever the swell is happening.
            </p>

            <h2>Where I'm at</h2>
            <p>
                Based in Israel. Spending a lot of time thinking about how AI is
                reshaping how brands and publishers understand real audience engagement.
                More on that soon.
            </p>

            <div class="about-links">
                <a href="/consulting">Work with me →</a>
                <a href="/art">See my art →</a>
                <a href="/contact">Get in touch →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</Layout>

<style>
.about-float-photo {
    float: right;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin: 0.5rem 0 2rem 3rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}

.about-body {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem var(--margin);
}

.about-title {
    font-family: var(--font-sans-serif);
    font-variant: small-caps;
    font-weight: var(--font-light);
    font-size: 4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-base);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}

.about-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.about-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-base);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.about-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans-serif);
    font-variant: small-caps;
    font-weight: var(--font-normal);
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    text-transform: lowercase;
}

.about-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}

.about-links a {
    font-family: var(--font-sans-serif);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.about-links a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

@media (max-width: 500px) {
    .about-float-photo {
        float: none;
        display: block;
        width: 140px;
        height: 140px;
        margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    }
}
</style>
